      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Salinity Tolerance Pane</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">This pane is on the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Farm_Crop_Properties_Dialog_Bo" styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Farm Land Use Properties</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">CROP_SALINITY_TOLERANCE specifies each Crop&apos;s salinity tolerance (ECe) in Electrical Conductivity (EC) in units of deciSiemens per meter (dS/m) ***NOT MODEL UNITS!!!</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Note 1 dS/m = 640 ppm = 640 mg/L</text></para>
